{"tid":718191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"太古城 槍擊案續","createTime":"2018-06-26T15:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T15:17:14.000Z","uid":176763,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c80069add56a34197d13d96dd630eb49aeec1ea8","tid":718191,"uid":176763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:08:46.000Z","msg":"Source : <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180626&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58367529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180626%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58367529&d=jbrgomOfy58J3%2FUUrHu67Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e06ec337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180626%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58367529&h=d03bf03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180626&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58367529</a><br />\n【槍擊爭產】女疑兇外婆留下<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">南豐新邨</span></span>單位 引爆血腥爭產<br />\n<br />\n太古城發生的史無前例槍殺親戚血案，背後隱藏着一個中產大家庭的爭產事件。《蘋果》追查後發現，女疑兇深信其離世的外婆留有一個位於鰂魚涌南豐新邨單位，懷疑遭血案中詹氏四兄弟姐妹所侵吞，才引發這場血腥槍擊案。<br />\n<br />\n據知，女疑兇的母親阿卿的詹氏一家至少有6兄弟姐妹，除了長子為養子外，阿卿為大女，其弟妹順序為少芬、前駒、鎮基、小慧等等，一直相安無事，惟至女疑兇外婆離世後，留有一幢物業作遺產，理應由他們兄弟姐妹平分，可是女疑兇懷疑當中有人從中所梗，遲遲未有處理遺產分配；又懷疑遺產執行人不但「更改遺囑」，且還「向政府虛假申報」物業估值，更嚴重故意拖延遺囑執行。<br />\n<br />\n直至其母2015年病逝後，女疑兇卻發現有人開始執行遺囑，令其母喪失分家產的機會，為此她曾要向政府部門介入調查真相。而其矛頭直指今次血案中，目前傷勢危始的四舅父鎮基，女疑兇去年就為此向四舅父提出質詢，又直指他將外婆的物業單位估值調低，因而對四名阿姨及舅父一直懷恨在心。<br />\n<br />\n女疑兇甚至懷母親病死疑點重重，她事後質疑醫院有失誤，認為負責的醫生要為母親的死負責，其後她更在網頁中寫千字文大控訴。<br />\n<br />\n為咗咁嘅樓就開槍 傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b917f608a54a796892f459cd91ed47225f990a80","tid":718191,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:09:24.000Z","msg":"有無美國巴打係熟支槍? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a479045a0939d8bde5caace6145b43dd445a8319","tid":718191,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12b6f4b5d9f8ccc0bba8446925c3636ac65c3001","tid":718191,"uid":176763,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/231131_41121d9befeba2cc262e219f6ec3dca0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F231131_41121d9befeba2cc262e219f6ec3dca0.png&h=72795a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc2c5ebceae6d1fa4f0b134de164e0461e545d1","tid":718191,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:12:10.000Z","msg":"個怨婦疑心重到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253e2463dd977c3b3d1e35b6e7f7854a616dca4f","tid":718191,"uid":176763,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a479045a0939d8bde5caace6145b43dd445a8319","tid":718191,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"值得去殺人？"},{"pid":"0baa656e2e1eac68477a05c212f2ad8e9a7e36a6","tid":718191,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"係囉  依家唔撚憂啦  <br />\n<br />\n下半世都有地方住   廢中女真醒目   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b5cb0feebab7eb22904839f0c44473b959187f","tid":718191,"uid":176763,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"南豐行撚到去太古城殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522baae942406f4535cc3b0